{"tid":692210,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤開售】葉太：「香港樓價癲架」 擬2,000萬購3房","createTime":"2018-06-06T12:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T17:00:22.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27ce3020db933a7c1422b9e7237c0434f707f07f","tid":692210,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"【新盤開售】葉太：「香港樓價癲架」 擬2,000萬購3房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180606/large/1528263541_b03a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180606%2Flarge%2F1528263541_b03a.jpg&h=9b16d8b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準買家葉太居住將軍澳，是次陪同30幾歲的阿仔買樓，打算購入3房戶，樓價約2,000萬元。首期主要由阿仔畀，她亦有幫補部份首期，問及阿仔做邊行，她只係話「打工仔」一個。問及點睇本港樓價，她認為「香港樓價癲架，成日話跌最後都係升」。"},{"pid":"0060a516bfd629cd8f953d722d18d0b75898b4bd","tid":692210,"uid":41204,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"典型中國農村大媽樣"},{"pid":"63c620d1017ccfa1e7a5b9c6cd4f92f054e099d0","tid":692210,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43cf98cac869124f7fab8453be8dcae950782944","tid":692210,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"阿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}